premise_source_doc_sentence: Past voice actor guests have included Wally Wingert  (  Sideburn and Mirage from Transformers : Robots In Disguise  )  and Neil Kaplan  (  Optimus Prime and Ro-Tor , Transformers : Robots In Disguise  )  , David Kaye  (  Megatron from Beast Wars , Beast Machines , Transformers : Armada , Transformers : Energon , Transformers : Cybertron and Optimus Prime in Transformers : Animated  )  , G1 actor Dan Gilvezan in 2008  (  Bumblebee  )  and for 2009 Beast Wars actor Ian James Corlett and G1 actor Gregg Berger .

Archer was the Design VP on the Transformers brand , a role that essentially made him the highest-ranking creative Transformers staffer on the Hasbro side of the business  (  Transformers are produced in partnership with Takara  )  .

Some homages to Aaron include the Transformers movie toy Longarm having `` Orson 's Towing '' on the door , the early name for Universe Skalor being listed as `` Archerbot '' , and the Transformers : Animated character `` Angry Archer '' .

He briefly provided art for Transformers : Generation 2 , drawing three pages of Transformers : Generation 2 # 2 as a favour to Furman and editor Rob Tokar when the original artist , Derek Yaniger , fell behind .
